quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  54,7,"Jaasu…ďe e ndaar…óe, hi…ďe yaltira e genaale …óen faade ka √Īaawirde, wano kanuuji carotoo…ói, hakkee hawjere."
  54,8,"He√Īanii…ďe noddoowo on ka √Īaawirde. Heefer…ďe …ďen wi'a: ndee …óoo ko √Īalaande sattunde. Tawde hinde wonnde e ca…óeele e kulhuli."
  54,9,"Ado …ďee yeddu…ďe ma …óoo an Nulaa…óo, hari yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen yeddiino. ∆Āe fenni ko Men nuli kon jeyaa…óo Amen on Nuuhu e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'i woo: ko jinnaa…óo ! …ďe purii mo noone fow wiide si o accaali noddugol …ďe."
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, wonnde : yim…ďe am …ďen foolii lam, …ďe ja…ďanaali lam. Faaboram jippinirgol leopte e dow ma…ď…ďe."
  54,11,"Men udditiri dammbu…óe kammu ngun, ndiyam saa∆īay…óam jokkondira."
  54,12,"Men tu…ď…ďiniri leydi ndin …ďulli ndiyam. Ndiyam …óam ka kammu e …óam ka leydi fottiri yamiroore Allah hoddiranoonde ko …ďooyi. ∆äam yooli fow, si wanna …ďe Allah da…ónunoo …ďe."
  54,13,"Men roondorii Nuuhu e laana lesaaka marka alluwe e peŇče. Men da…óndi mo kanko e wondunoo…ďe e ma…ď…ďe …ďen yoolagol."
  54,14,"Ka laana no dogira e mororonje maayo e ngon, ndenka Amen. ∆äum ko faabo Nuuhu ngon non e ko yim…ďe makko …ďen fenni mo kon, …ďe yeddi ko o addani …ďe kon immorde ka Allah."
  54,15,"Gom…óii Men fillitorii kon ko Men leptirnoo …ďe, waaju e tasakuyee. Taw non si woodi waajitry…óo …óum?"
  54,16,"Taskii ko honno lepte Am …óen wa'unoo? E ko honno jertinol Am halkugol …ďe ngol wa'unoo?"
  54,17,"Gom…óii Men newinirii Alquur'aanaare nden waajitorgol. Hara no woodi waajitoray…óo tasakuyeeji mayre."
  54,18,"Aadi'en fennuno Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on Huudu. Onon yim…ďe Makka, teskee ko honno lepte Am …óen wa'unoo e ma…ď…ďe? Tasko…óon kadi ko honno Mi jertinirnoo …óe wo…ó…ďe goo?"
  54,19,"Men wurtu e ma…ď…ďe henndu tii…óundu …ďuu…ďol, e √Īalaande …ďaleere, duumodaynde e ma…ď…ďe haa ka Jahiimi."
  54,20,"Hindu wippitira yim…ďe …ďen e leydi ndin, ndu bugora …ďe ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen, wa si tawii ko …ďe da∆ī∆īe …óoofaade e jayru."
  54,21,"Taskee onon yim…ďe Makka …ďen, ko honno lepte Am …óen wa'unoo e ma…ď…ďe? Tasko…óon kadi ko honno Mi jertinirnoo …óe wo…ó…ďe goo?"
  54,22,"Gom…óii Men newinirii Alquur'aanaare nden waajitorgol. Hara no woodi waajitoray…óo tasakuyeeji mayre."
  54,23,"Samuuda'en fennuno waaju Nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on Saalih (yo o his)."
  54,24,"∆Āe wi'i hi…ďe yedda : kere ko ne…ó…óo gooto e amen woni ko men jokkata? Si men wa…óii …óum, haray ontuma men wonii woopu…ďe sari'a oo√Īiini e mun, woni kadi e tampere."
  54,25,"Hara ko e makko wahayu on jippinaa hakkunde amen? O heertora …óum hakkunde amen? Si ko woni, ko fenoowo nii, townitii…óo."
  54,26,"Aray …ďe annda √Ďalnde Janngo, ko hommbo woni fenoowo townitii…óo on? Anndon si Saalih kaa ko kam…ďe?"
  54,27,"Ko Men yaltiniroo…ďe ngelooba ndewa mbam ka fetere, Men wurtira mba e ma…ď…ďe, jarribagol …ďe. Aynitu…ďe …ďe an Saalih, tinaa ko …ďe wa…óata mba e ko …ďe huuwetee ontuma, mu√Ī√Īo…óaa lorra ma…ď…ďe."